1. No validations on all fields except Name and Email fields (User can place order by enetring only name and pohone)
2. User can enter the string value in Quantity field.
3. Quantity field can accept the negative values.(User can place order by entering -1 quantity)
4. "Toppings 1" and "Toppings 2" dropdown fields are not clear after clicking on the reset button.
5. Displayed "NAN" when user enters the Invalid Quantity. (E.g ABCD or /*+%*&^)
6. User can select both payment options at a time.

